= <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> Congress

Stresemann has called an emergency party congress within the <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> over the contentious issue of a merger with <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>. The Liberal Association has already made significant strides in laying the groundwork for a <span style="color: #FFCC00;">united liberal party</span>, including the creation of a national framework and the drafting of a middle-class-oriented policy platform broadly supported by both parties.

However, the right wing of the <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span>, led by Ernst Scholz, remains the final stumbling block towards a <span style="color: #FFCC00;">united liberal party</span>. They are determined to oppose the merger, wielding their substantial influence over the party and industrialists to rally against it.

