The momentum towards liberal unity has proven too great for the few holdouts within the <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span>'s right wing to stand against. The party has officially voted to approve the merger with the <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>, who have also done the same. Both parties will now work together to establish the framework of the new <span style="color: #FFCC00;">Liberal People's Party</span>.